    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>blanched peas</strong> to a pot, cover them with<strong> boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 1 min or until they're warmed through, then drain and return to the pot with a knob of<strong> butter</strong></p><p>Mash the peas until they come together nicely – these are your <strong>mushy peas</strong></p>",
