      "instruction": "<p>Remove the skewer[s] from the <strong>battered sausage[s] </strong>and serve with the <strong>chips </strong>and<strong> mushy</strong> <strong>peas</strong> to the side</p><p>Serve the <strong>curry</strong> <strong>sauce</strong> in a pot to the side for dipping</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
